values:
So I'm free.  After some nasty Chinese people attacked me and stuffed me in a box, and the jet noises.  I was placed on a truck for most of the day.  After the truck noise, there was some gentle handling and a weird car sound (dare I say it was British?).

Anyway, I was removed from my prison to this bright light, and the first thing I see is beard.  I was saved!
Some crazy Chinese man threw me in a box and I can't get out.  I hear a truck, and jet engines, and I'm scared.  Someone please come rescue me!
